{
  "stem": "8892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we arrived there, Poland-- I just found out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a-- it, it wasn't a ghetto for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a Polish concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all five of us, all the five cousins-- Weiss girls and my sister,",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--all the way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Plaszow, when we arrived there, our amazement was that the Polish people were dressed normally-- western clothes, boots on girls, beautiful hair.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they look normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we arrive, we're looking like-- [SIGHS] like caricatures, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Crazy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were the first Hungarian-- we found that out after that-- to be transferred to, to Plaszow, which was all Polish people till then.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So [SIGHS] when we arrived there, they ask if you arbeiten, what can-- you know, what can you do?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my sister, who hated sewing all her life, she volunteers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she says, I sew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so does my other three cousins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, two cousin, who really were dressmakers, they say that their arbeiten is Schneider, schneidering.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they are sewers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they get separated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we're in a camp, but in the same barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put them in a different direction.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were working in a munition factory, making soldier's uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the one who didn't have trade, like me and my oldest cousin-- she was the oldest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That time she was about 26.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was at my height, so she always stayed front of me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- no, behind me, because my sister was the tallest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was front, then I was behind her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how we were lined up, always the same way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were assigned to work outside that ghetto, where they had the German soldiers building barns for the horses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were assigned to wheelbarrow the cement for the bricklayers.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
